---
name: anthropic-agent-test
description: Anthropic agent loop integration test
model:
  id: claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929
  provider: anthropic
  apiType: chat
  connection:
    kind: key
    apiKey: ${env:ANTHROPIC_API_KEY}
  options:
    maxOutputTokens: 256
tools:
  - name: get_weather
    kind: function
    description: Get the current weather for a city
    parameters:
      - name: location
        kind: string
        description: City name
        required: true
inputs:
  question:
    kind: string
    default: What is the weather in Seattle?
template:
  format:
    kind: jinja2
  parser:
    kind: prompty
---
system:
You are a helpful assistant. Use tools when needed. After getting tool results, summarize the answer.

user:
{{question}}
